Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\b1\fs90\an5\bord0\pos(1650,955)\c&HF0F2EF&}希尔莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.86,Sub-JP,,0,0,0,,え?なんでこの3人だけなの?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,诶?为什么就我们仨人
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.44,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur1\an6\p1\c&HB56B40&\pos(1359.4,111)}m 550 800 l 1100 800 1100 1000 550 1000
